{"tid":127566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民hot talk】 《大時代》對白神預測！恥笑撐警歪理","createTime":"2017-02-20T07:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T08:06:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fec80b1a9db6818f13a36a1e5ab7101afd7ca1d0","tid":127566,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170220/19934338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170220%2F19934338&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=840e6aed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170220%2F19934338&h=01f8b1c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170220/19934338</a><br />\n<br />\n【網民hot talk】<br />\n《大時代》對白神預測！恥笑撐警歪理<br />\n<br />\n42,322<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n七警案於本周二宣判，裁定各被告襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成。7名被告在庭上均以佔領期間工作壓力大，以及案件毀事業和家庭作求情理由，包括與拍拖7年的女友分手、與未婚妻婚禮叫停、本來仕途一片光明等。有網民即回帶大師級編劇韋家輝的經典電視劇《大時代》劇情，認為兩者有異曲同功之妙。由鄭少秋飾演的大奸角丁蟹因打死人被控謀殺，他在庭上以歪理自辯，稱家中有4名兒子和年老的母親等候自己照顧，「呢件案嘅重點唔係我有冇殺人，而係&mdash;&mdash;浪子回頭金不換！」惟在劇中即被法官糾正，「我提醒陪審團，呢件案嘅重點，絕對係被告有冇殺人」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民不禁震驚「點解現實可以痴線過電視劇」，有撐警團體人士指七警只是錯在被鏡頭拍攝到犯案經過，又指責法官故意判重刑侮辱警隊，有網民嘲諷指以他們的理解，「呢件案嘅重點係佢地拉人行私刑嘅地方唔夠暗，同法官係洋人」。<br />\n<br />\n【網民咁睇】<br />\nBonnie Ho：警隊丁蟹化！<br />\nIssac Chu：呢單案重點唔係我地有無暗角打鑊，而係佢挑釁我地<br />\nDenise Ng：韋家輝真是神<br />\nWallace Lo：成班警察都係丁蟹！丁蟹打完方進新仲同方進新講：「你點解要迫我出手!?你明知我出手重就唔好激我啦！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n律師：特赦例原用於未成年犯<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n收緊住院保險　AIA致函醫生疑干預"},{"pid":"b75e0b8f8dbab073d1bdacbe47d3029dd589acf3","tid":127566,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170220/org/1487533801_db11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170220%2Forg%2F1487533801_db11.jpg&h=64bc93b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"183368816df0e9610f7166d2fa81c406079d61d8","tid":127566,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee06fc414ff8a9e9e9b56add4f604cb9f357a7fc","tid":127566,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都好慘"},{"pid":"141cd9b9b1159c2694be87a6d96d0b8841837d10","tid":127566,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都好慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378e2db932dafc754ccad411a1cfedff985f45d6","tid":127566,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都好慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揀咗慳妹抌低你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74afc6cd92aa07b590a0a59acad7f7a905b95d1","tid":127566,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都好慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揀咗慳妹抌低你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要， 佢